Red Zone

Slider buckets
Random: yard line selected from +20 to +1
Fringe: +30 to +21
High Red Zone: +20 to +12
Low Red Zone: +11 to +4
Goal Line: +3 to +1

Yard Line (if Yard Line = Random)
Weighted by the Red Zone yard probability table (30 down to 1), filtered to the bucket range, then re-normalized.

Score Differential options
Random, +3, +2, +1, 0, -1 to -8

Hash
Random (weighted per Red Zone hash rules) or user-selected.
